# v0.5.3 Release Plan

**Theme**: Codebase cleanup & hardening — dead code removal, security posture improvement, and configuration consistency.

**Goal**: Reduce technical debt accumulated through v0.5.0–v0.5.2 by removing dead code, consolidating duplicate modules, fixing service configuration issues, and tightening network exposure. No new features.

---

## Status Update (from v0.5.2 completion)

**Already Completed in v0.5.2:**
- ✅ Blockchain Explorer enhancements (pagination, copy-to-clipboard, skip empty blocks, non-empty blocks endpoint)
- ✅ Marketplace website integration (marketplace.html, marketplace.js, CSS styling, navigation updates)
- ✅ Explorer analytics (activity timeline, network stats, provider reputation, top addresses)
- ✅ Dedicated detail pages (block.html, tx.html, search.html)
- ✅ Real-time features (live feed ticker, auto-refresh)
