- 🟡 Root-level artifacts: `marketplace.db`, `create_sample_offers.py`, `create_sample_offers_simple.py`, `pyproject.toml.new`
- 🟡 24 services binding to 0.0.0.0 (internal services should use 127.0.0.1)
