## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Deleting handlers/ breaks something | Medium | Verify no imports first, keep backup |
| Changing 0.0.0.0 to 127.0.0.1 breaks remote access | High | Test each service after change, document in NETWORK_POLICY.md |
| Removing systemd units breaks dependencies | Low | Check `Wants=`/`Requires=` in other units first |
| CLI config consolidation breaks imports | Medium | Update all imports in same commit |

